<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.7">
<l>mallē poruta tiraḷtōl maṇavāḷīr</l>
<l>allē yaṟintōm nummaṉat tiṉkaruttai</l>
<l>collā toḻiyīr coṉṉapō tiṉālvārīr</l>
<l>ellē yituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Beloved with strong arms that battled the wrestlers,</l>
<l>We knew in the night your mind’s desire.</l>
<l>You did not leave without saying [a time; but] you did not come</l>
<l rend="indent">by the time [you] said.</l>
<l>What is all this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
